{"tid":1738473,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[黃色經濟圈]你買我就代你捐一半","createTime":"2019-11-19T09:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T16:51:18.000Z","uid":287547,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cf62bec6a78083e7606f724fea8d714576b2bba7","tid":1738473,"uid":287547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:07:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>前言:</strong><br />\n<br />\n係上一個post, 本來想推廣一個手足可以以成本價買野既商業方式<br />\n但好多手足都認為會被POPO藍絲<span style=\"color: red;\">濫用</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係多番考量後, 我們決定推出另一種方式:<br />\n<br />\n<strong>理念:</strong><br />\n<br />\n主要因為希望做到:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1.能持續穩定地有捐款支持手足義士<br />\n<br />\n2.招聘被捕義士, 保障義士的生活同發展</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>定價方式:</strong><br />\n<br />\n商品定價 <br />\n-定價比絕大部分市場價<span style=\"color: red;\">便宜</span>, 大家支持手足同時也節省開支<br />\n<br />\n<strong>利潤分配:</strong><br />\n<br />\n-<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所有利潤的一半將會代大家捐到 612  or 星火 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">單數月份: 星火 <br />\n雙數月份:  612基金</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">捐款金額會於產品頁面顯示 ,絕對公開透明:</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Y0nYHe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Y0nYHe.png&h=c6ec4653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-另一半利潤會用作<span style=\"color: red;\">支援企業持續發展</span><br />\n<br />\n依然主要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">優先招聘被捕手足</span></span>, 會參照&rdquo;光時&rdquo;做法<br />\n<br />\n<strong>後言:</strong><br />\n<br />\n另外, 係呢度要同各位係10月&amp; 11月 已經係本店買左野既手足致歉.<br />\n因為做唔切, 未能充分準備, 導致大家等左長時間先收到貨, 十分抱歉.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>簡介:</strong><br />\n<br />\n網店名稱 :<strong> 有得揀</strong><br />\n營業形式 : <strong>網店</strong><br />\n網店地址 :<a href=\"http://www.unitchoice.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.unitchoice.com&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=3d160eae\" target=\"_blank\">www.unitchoice.com</a><br />\n商品種類 : 電子及手機配件<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/unitChoice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FunitChoice&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=b55273df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/unitChoice</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家加入Telegram分享你任何意見<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/K_lZU0XUm0Q0lP-apCF_1A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FK_lZU0XUm0Q0lP-apCF_1A&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=fb8f40bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/K_lZU0XUm0Q0lP-apCF_1A</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>P.S.</strong><br />\n另外, 因為剛開業既關係, 由下單到發貨需時大約一星期, 希望大家體諒支持<br />\n<br />\nP牌推唔郁, 大家幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港! 時代革命!!!! </span></span>"},{"pid":"3b50def0a12bd70251af2aa58813d98f5b731fbf","tid":1738473,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:08:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df0bf2fc873b7703266e31f382d4c8900a20e317","tid":1738473,"uid":12251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:13:26.000Z","msg":"JOYROOM 中國野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6124f106c931acb86c6ee98c46ebc175bc21f92e","tid":1738473,"uid":287547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df0bf2fc873b7703266e31f382d4c8900a20e317","tid":1738473,"uid":12251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:13:26.000Z","msg":"JOYROOM 中國野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:18:11.000Z","msg":"咁咩價位都有 先至有得揀架ma<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60551a062ca9faa9b3602cb9ab46c342e47e179c","tid":1738473,"uid":245301,"like"